title: Ugly Kid Joe - Uglier Than They Used Ta Be  2015 320ak
description:
Uglier Than They Used ta Be is the fourth album by the band Ugly Kid Joe.

On February 4, 2015, Ugly Kid Joe started a crowd funding effort through pledgemusic.com to fund their new album, Uglier Than They Used ta Be. The album was completely funded by February 20. 

Uglier Than They Used Ta Be is the first full-length album put out by the band in 19 years. To the release date it was funded to 201%.
